# Deploy in HSE cluster

###  _cd_ to _deploy_ folder
``` cd deploy ```

### Connect to cluster
```gcloud container clusters get-credentials hse-cluster-01 --zone us-central1-a --project light-reality-205619```

### Deploy platform-auth
```helm --set "global.env=hse" upgrade --install platformregistryapi platformregistryapi```




#Deploy in stagging and dev clusters

Dev :
	- helm --set "global.env=dev" install platformregistryapi --name=platformregistryapi

Stage :
	- helm --set "global.env=stage" install platformregistryapi --name=platformregistryapi
